iror narsa qilishimni xohlasangiz, iltimos, menga yozing.</em><br />● Your party last weekend was the best yet. - <em>O'tgan hafta oxiri sizning ziyofatingiz yaxshi bo`ldi.</em> <br />● If you need anything in your study, please let me know. - <em>Agar o'qishingizda biror narsa kerak bo'lsa, iltimos, menga xabar bering.</em><br />● I hope you will give me the chance to return your kindness. - <em>Umid qilamanki, siz menga yaxshiligingizni sizga ham qaytarish imkoniyatini berasiz.</em></p>
</details>
